:todo:
use utf8 chars through :digraphs: to take notes on individual projects
and note types.
E.g.:
* ♔ for most rewarding things (such as reading "pattern recognition"
  (mumford) and Tsallis)
* ☥ for more relevant contributions
* ☯ for equilibrium matters
* ☠ for dead ends or wrong ways
* ☮ for socially-engaged stuff
* ☘ for opportunities
* ☨ for transcendental stuff
* Ⓐ for political and notes (e.g. experiments)
* symbols are written 1-6 times, as a rating of the characteristic.
* E.g.:
  * Espiritualidade instrumental ☮☮☮☮ 
* make mappings with Alt TTM


